<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="External_links">External links</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Iraiyanar_Akapporul&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: External links"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.tamilnation.org/literature/pmunicode/mp301.htm">Full text</a> of the nūṟpās, together with an extract of the commentary on the first verse (in Tamil)</li></ul>
